name: The Little Talks Jotter Pack
description:
Jot things down with these handmade blank jotters that feature images from Nova Scotia and India.

The covers of the jotters are printed with archival quality, pigment based inks on matte photo paper. The jotters are packaged in cellophane sleeves for protection.

DIMENSIONS 
Card measures 3.5 in. by 5.5 in.

PAGES
20 blank pages (40 front and back), 25% cotton paper

SHIPPING 
Ships in a rigid flat board envelope to prevent bending. 
Please view my shop's Policies for estimated shipping times before purchasing.

*Please note shipping costs are for regular post only. 
**All photographs are my own.

name: Any 3 Photo Greeting Cards
description:

Mix + match to your heart's content! You can also choose the same card 3 times.
